Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit fooling around, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave you behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.08,0:02:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he shaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even on a mission, I can do it whenever I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.04,0:02:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must still be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what happened yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yamato sure is taking a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. How far could he have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Captain Yamato...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yamato, don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.51,0:03:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry. I couldn't resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me, you're scary enough without any pranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're a very easy target, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Captain, getting back to the topic \Nat hand, why would they defile a grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually grave-robbers target the tombs of rich\N people hoping to steal the treasures inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in this case, the body and the treasures were left intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These incidents have been occurring frequently within a 50-60 meter radius of the Fire Temple, where we're headed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the ones who requested this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And since they specifically requested Konoha's\N help dealing with these tomb raids,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling there's more to this than meets the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are actually four hidden tombs in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the raiders are after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's a strong possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! What do you mean by hidden tomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.56,0:04:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in death, a ninja's body contains all sorts of information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In some cases, that information can be worth a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your fight with Sasori, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He turned the Third Kazekage's corpse into a puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.25,0:04:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more capable the ninja, the more use they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to keep the bodies from being stolen or misused, barriers are often erected around the tombs, and their locations are kept secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I meant by a hidden tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there are some really awesome ninja buried there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, especially these four.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The information contained in their bodies is unbelievably valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there's also another possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that the tomb wasn't broken into from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the corpse came back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He actually believed what Captain Yamato said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta keep practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.81,0:05:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A group from the Fire Temple will be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.25,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have a seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.02,0:06:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's room over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make too much noise, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. He's scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we stop at the wrong landmark?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Sai wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise we might miss them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay by Naruto's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit trying to scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When your friend is frightened or scared, try\N gently placing your hand on their shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to show them in a warm, friendly way that they're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is much harder than I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I thought it was a good idea-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't swing that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, when your friend misunderstands you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanging around with you is too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough. I'm gonna go find Sakura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you... Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did I do wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:09:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand how Sai's brain works...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be the tomb raiders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A warthog?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I've seen one of these before...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:13.52,Gray,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(633,397)}Forbidden
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A barrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hidden tomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The coffin is gone. I'm too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.88,0:12:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the tomb raider?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Juuha Shou{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:32.53,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Juuha Shou: Beast Wave Strike)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tajuu Kage Bunshin no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Juuha Shou{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. His wind techniques are tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wind? Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you also have wind ele-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Repent now. I'll give you three seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up. Time for your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's getting punished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kage Bunshin no Jutsu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Juuha Shou{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Juuha Reppuu Shou{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:14.35,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(Juuha Reppuu Shou: Beast Wave Violent Wind Strike)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.70,0:16:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiriku-sama, you were right to be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got worried about the hidden tomb on the way\N to meet our guests, and came to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.01,0:16:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I did, the barrier had been torn down,\N the coffin was stolen, and he was inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you trying to pin your crimes on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the real thief, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?! You were in the tomb first!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the coffin was already gone when I went in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.77,0:16:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? Prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick your ass, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your best shot, loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat me, wuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brethren from Konoha, I am Chiriku of the Fire Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:17:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for the mistake in establishing the rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Konoha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sora, a monk in training, also from the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora-kun, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the captain of this team, Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Naruto, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already said it, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need any help from Konoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.02,0:17:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiriku-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitane-sama's coffin has been stolen, with no traces of forced entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To break the barrier so easily, they\N must be extremely capable shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the enemies are that skilled, we definitely\N have good reason to call on Konoha for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two go back and make arrangements\N to defend the remaining three tombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, strengthen the temple's security and start\N preparations for an emergency situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us return to the Fire Temple for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is your chakra wind-natured?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ignore me, I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know about that technique you used!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was this hand-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exactly like that dream I had...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.72,0:20:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you gonna sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.64,0:20:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be late for our mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you live in such a filthy room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Half-eaten ramen on the floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and expired milk left out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you clean up for once?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.65,0:20:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto, you stupid slob!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.49,0:21:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's real... It actually exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks-!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.51,0:21:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, damn it, damn it, damn it, I'll kill him-!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H282828&\4c&H282828&}Sora, how could you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes. I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him if it's the last thing I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not, or you'll be punished for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Chiriku-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.48,0:22:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Shubi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.69,0:22:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is leading a group to the other three hidden tombs:\N Nauma-sama's, Tou'u-sama's and Seito-sama's.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all skilled monks from our Temple.\N If anything happens, we'll know immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.05,0:22:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitane-sama is conducting an investigation\N of the area, and the others are standing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.46,0:22:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have reinforced the temple, and everyone\N is prepared for an emergency situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can relax for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.10,0:22:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.38,0:22:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with his attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.26,0:22:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.94,0:23:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have returned. These four are from\N Konoha and have come at my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. I am Captain Yamato.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.57,0:23:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With me are Sakura, Sai and Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Konoha? That's reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave everything to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're prepared to take action anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have to wait for the news from our ninja monks in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, please follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what they want to use the stolen body for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.89,0:23:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Either he wants the information within the body, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.53,0:24:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuchiyose Edo Tensei{\i1}!{\i0}
