Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.64,0:24:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems the third one failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.97,0:24:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.92,0:24:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They may want to use the actual body itself, like Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.78,0:24:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I doubt there's anyone around here who uses techniques like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.90,0:24:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the guys inside these four hidden tombs\N must've been pretty awesome, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.16,0:24:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.59,0:24:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were indeed "awesome".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.78,0:24:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, they were good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.62,0:24:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the Fire Temple in the middle,\N to the east, west, south and north...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.79,0:24:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lie the graves of Nauma, Seito, Tou'u, and Kitane.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.89,0:25:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were also members of The Twelve Ninja Guardians.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.61,0:25:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Twelve Ninja Guardians?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.53,0:25:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.14,0:25:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've only heard the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.37,0:25:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real? Are they famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.24,0:25:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you either know of them or you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.65,0:25:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Twelve Ninja Guardians is an organization whose members are gathered from all across the Fire Country to protect its Feudal Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.87,0:25:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't protecting the Fire country our job as Konoha shinobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.26,0:25:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting the Fire Country is the responsibility of our village, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.10,0:25:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But therein lies the difference. Konoha is an organization that protects the entire country, whereas the Feudal Lord is just one man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.34,0:25:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.45,0:25:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to protect a country, you need\N to protect the top, the Feudal Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.12,0:25:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Twelve Ninja Guardians were formed\N by people who shared that view.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.48,0:25:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was very young back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.28,0:26:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was all too eager to sacrifice my life for\N the Fire Country, and I joined the Twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.60,0:26:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Chiriku-san, you're-
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.56,0:26:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be, anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.49,0:26:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Asuma-san is also a former member of The Twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.45,0:26:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma? Is he doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.91,0:26:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing great. Actually, he just\N gave me some advice for my training!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.01,0:26:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.37,0:26:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.15,0:26:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then these incidents are, to you and Asuma-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.51,0:26:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,equivalent to your friends' graves being defiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.13,0:26:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those four gave their lives for the Fire Country at a young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.40,0:27:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few members of the Twelve tried to stage a coup d'etat,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.06,0:27:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the resulting clash resulted in the entire group falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.17,0:27:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coup d'etat means that a person or group tried to usurp power and change a country to match their own ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.88,0:27:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.07,0:27:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to protect the Fire Country." A simple wish that resulted in serious disagreements between the Twelve Ninja Guardians.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.36,0:27:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. So that means-!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.80,0:27:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means they didn't want to leave\N the Fire Country in Konoha's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.81,0:27:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd rather have used military power to\N create a country with themselves at the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.04,0:27:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really! You can't let people get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.09,0:27:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.41,0:27:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.79,0:27:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut {\i1}up{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.60,0:28:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are correct. They wanted to dismantle Konoha village,\N and place all military power under the Feudal Lord's control.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.12,0:28:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their plan got as far as preparing to move the Feudal Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.84,0:28:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at the same time, they had prepared\N to attack several other countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.57,0:28:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They had?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.85,0:28:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't care about the fine balance of\N peace between the Five Great Countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.54,0:28:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,believing that true peace would only come if the Fire Country conquered the world and united all nations under its banner.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.87,0:28:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.69,0:28:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We tried all kinds of negotiations, but in the end, war is war.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.86,0:28:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Feudal Lord realized how far they had taken things, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.64,0:29:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the six who staged the coup died.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.46,0:29:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kitane, Nauma, Tou'u and Seito were sacrificed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.43,0:29:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could have known that happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.77,0:29:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In these hidden tombs lay the friends of Chiriku and Asuma-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.07,0:29:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If one of Naruto or Sakura's friends, such as \NSasuke-kun, died, and his body was stolen...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.60,0:29:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.50,0:29:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let the person who stole \NKitane-san's body to get away with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.95,0:29:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.93,0:29:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The men are beginning their evening practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.51,0:30:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freakin' Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.44,0:30:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your stances.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.85,0:30:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.00,0:30:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.24,0:30:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.34,0:30:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.94,0:30:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.31,0:31:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.23,0:31:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.19,0:31:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.38,0:31:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is this good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.14,0:31:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... Are you trying to mess with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.24,0:31:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.67,0:31:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno what kinda training that was, but all I saw was this.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.63,0:31:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.08,0:31:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.70,0:31:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were making fun of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.00,0:31:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno why, but I didn't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.65,0:31:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto! You moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.92,0:31:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Naruto, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.12,0:31:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.39,0:31:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a better name.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.80,0:31:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kaimyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.80,0:31:50.95,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}(A new name created by Buddhist priests for a recently departed person.)
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.03,0:31:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaimyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.95,0:31:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.37,0:32:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're finally serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.06,0:32:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's more like the strength you showed me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.71,0:32:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're making me angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.76,0:32:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, aren't you getting too worked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.06,0:32:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.15,0:33:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.62,0:33:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like his power just drained away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.33,0:33:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes... Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.81,0:33:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.11,0:33:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...do you have eyes like-?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.46,0:33:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.98,0:34:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, I can't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.24,0:34:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I couldn't think of a kaimyou for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.49,0:34:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.67,0:34:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to wipe your sweat off.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.81,0:34:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! It's just...wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.53,0:34:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.07,0:35:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a kaimyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.72,0:35:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose it's like a nickname, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.57,0:35:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H282828&\4c&H282828&}But they're only for dead people-
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.86,0:35:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, like how you always try to think of nicknames?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.44,0:35:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a sign of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.08,0:35:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.31,0:35:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.16,0:35:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.93,0:35:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naoma-sama's tomb has been defiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.12,0:36:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Juuha Shou{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.73,0:36:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Juuha Reppuu Shou{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.22,0:36:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your techniques are awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.09,0:36:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you doing wind-element chakra manipulation?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.96,0:36:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.92,0:37:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I thought of coming here to give you a kaimyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.82,0:37:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll give you a nice kaimyou!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.78,0:37:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...Sora...Sora-chi, Souran, Sora-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.49,0:37:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, how dare you mock me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.12,0:37:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened back at the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.54,0:37:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You disgust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.63,0:37:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's how people thought of me when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.88,0:37:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.60,0:37:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?! So what...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.04,0:37:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I disgust them! But I don't give a rat's ass about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.21,0:38:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I disgust myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.26,0:38:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.09,0:38:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate my powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.87,0:38:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.15,0:38:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, I can't simply rid myself of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.10,0:38:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need them to get revenge for my\N father's death... To kill his murderer...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.84,0:38:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.55,0:38:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Momo Midori. Did something happen at a tomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.39,0:38:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto! Where were you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.64,0:38:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.86,0:38:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a report from the people that went to Nauma's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.57,0:38:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tomb had been broken into, and the corpse was removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.75,0:38:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.32,0:38:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, the other two will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.67,0:39:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready to move. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.40,0:39:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.60,0:39:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.75,0:39:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, time to beat the crap outta these grave robbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.79,0:39:46.60,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kodomo no koro mita niji wo
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.79,0:39:46.60,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,If I look up now for the rainbow I saw as a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.76,0:39:52.20,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ima miageru to nana iro de wa naku
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.76,0:39:52.20,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,there are no longer the seven colors,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.37,0:39:58.34,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yagate kiri ga kakari
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.37,0:39:58.34,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,only mist and fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.28,0:40:04.91,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jikan wa sugi kawatte yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.28,0:40:04.91,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,As time passes by, and the world around me changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.08,0:40:11.55,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kimi wo sagashitemo doko ni mo inai
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.08,0:40:11.55,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter where I search for you, you're nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.72,0:40:17.36,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Me wo toji, kokoro hiraite
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.72,0:40:17.36,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,So I close my eyes, and open my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.53,0:40:23.67,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}mata nagamete mitemo nanimo kawaranai no ka
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.53,0:40:23.67,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to know, if I gaze up again,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.83,0:40:29.44,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}tashikamete mitai
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.83,0:40:29.44,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,will things be different this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.31,0:40:36.31,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sunao ni narereba kono kiri ga hareru to
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.31,0:40:36.31,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe if I was more honest, the fog would fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.48,0:40:41.82,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}kokoro ni negai sou sakenderu
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.48,0:40:41.82,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,So I pray, screaming that wish deep within my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.62,0:40:48.62,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nanika wo nakushiteshimatta koto de sou
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.62,0:40:48.62,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,When you lose one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.69,0:40:54.13,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}te ni shita mono mo kitto arun darou
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.69,0:40:54.13,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,you gain another, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.60,0:41:01.00,ED3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dakedo mada bokura wa otona ni tomadoi
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.60,0:41:01.00,ED3up,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, no matter how often the adults confuse us,
