Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.88,0:41:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've received word from the Fire Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.46,0:41:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The four hidden tombs have already been raided by the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.49,0:41:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They got us. What's the situation now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.58,0:41:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Team Kakashi is heading to their location.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.07,0:41:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're after the actual bodies of the\N members of the Twelve Ninja Guardians, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.71,0:41:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're also unsure of what Orochimaru and Akatsuki are plotting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.93,0:41:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's the issue of Danzou-sama's loyalties...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.00,0:41:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've really got our hands full here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.19,0:41:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to do whatever we can!
