Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.61,0:41:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This week's question is:
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.41,0:41:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to smack the crap out of that wimp Sora, but the Fire Temple's his home turf. Anything I should know?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.18,0:41:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.17,0:41:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's such a jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.27,0:41:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.69,0:41:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fire Temple is Konoha's largest ninja temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.03,0:42:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an old temple with an ornate design and impregnable security.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.44,0:42:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ninja Monks are said to have the knowledge\N of sages, and use a wide variety of techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.83,0:42:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he's a former member of the Twelve Ninja\N Guardians, no one doubts Chiriku-san's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.89,0:42:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just noticed this, but how come so many\N of them haven't shaved their heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.31,0:42:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Well, they might just be apprentices-
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.86,0:42:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that makes sense! They're just trainees!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.21,0:42:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I said might-
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.70,0:42:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if he's just a trainee, I'll cut him some slack.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.97,0:42:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I think I'll go give him a few pointers!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.31,0:42:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess we answered his question... See you next time!
